name: Inventory of intertidal benthic diatoms of Gazi Bay (Kenya) sampled in September 1991
description: This dataset contains a list of intertidaldiatom species sampled at Gazi Bay (Kenya) in September 1991. Samples were taken from the upper 1 centimeter at each station using a Perspex insert tube (diameter 22mm). Identification of the diatoms was done on light- and electron microscopy.
